<ul>
  <li>design:
    <ul>
      <li>what it is, interventions, goals, constraints</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>the design process
    <ul>
      <li>what happens when</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>users
    <ul>
      <li>who they are, what they are like ‚Ä¶</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>scenarios
    <ul>
      <li>rich stories of design</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>navigation
    <ul>
      <li>finding your way around a system</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>iteration and prototypes
    <ul>
      <li>never get it right first time! 2</li>
    </ul>
