<p><br /></p>

<h2 id="interactions-and-interventions">Interactions and interventions</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Design interactions not just interfaces
    <ul>
      <li>not just the immediate interaction</li>
      <li>e.g. stapler in office ‚Äì technology changes interaction style
        <ul>
          <li>manual: write, print, staple, write, print, staple, ‚Ä¶</li>
          <li>electric: write, print, write, print, ‚Ä¶, staple</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Design interventions not just artefacts
    <ul>
      <li>not just the system, but also ‚Ä¶
        <ul>
          <li>documentation, manuals, tutorials</li>
          <li>what we say and do as well as what we make</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

<h2 id="what-is-design">What is design?</h2>

<p>Achieving goals within constraints</p>

<ul>
  <li>Goals - purpose
    <ul>
      <li>who is it for, why do they want it</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Constraints
    <ul>
      <li>materials, platforms</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Trade-offs</li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

<h2 id="for-humancomputer-interaction">for Human‚ÄìComputer Interaction</h2>

<p>Understand your materials</p>

<ul>
  <li>Understand computers
    <ul>
      <li>limitations, capacities, tools, platforms</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Understand people
    <ul>
      <li>psychological, social aspects</li>
      <li>human error</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>And their interaction ‚Ä¶</li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

<h2 id="to-err-is-human">To err is human</h2>

<ul>
  <li>accident reports ..
    <ul>
      <li>aircrash, industrial accident, hospital mistake</li>
      <li>enquiry ‚Ä¶ blames ‚Ä¶ ‚Äòhuman error‚Äô</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>but ‚Ä¶
    <ul>
      <li>concrete lintel breaks because too much weight</li>
      <li>blame ‚Äòlintel error‚Äô ? ‚Ä¶ no ‚Äì design error we know how concrete behaves under stress</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>human ‚Äòerror‚Äô is normal
    <ul>
      <li>we know how users behave under stress</li>
      <li>so design for it!</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>treat the user at least as well as physical materials!</li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

