<h2 id="steps">Steps‚Ä¶</h2>

<ul>
  <li>requirements
    <ul>
      <li>what is there and what is wanted ‚Ä¶</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>analysis
    <ul>
      <li>ordering and understanding</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>design
    <ul>
      <li>what to do and how to decide</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>iteration and prototyping
    <ul>
      <li>getting it right ‚Ä¶ and finding what is really needed!</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>implementation and deployment
    <ul>
      <li>making it and getting it out there</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

<h2 id="-but-how-can-i-do-it-all--">‚Ä¶ but how can I do it all ! !</h2>

<ul>
  <li>limited time =&gt; design trade-off</li>
  <li>usability?
    <ul>
      <li>finding problems and fixing them?</li>
      <li>deciding what to fix?</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>a perfect system is badly designed
    <ul>
      <li>too good =&gt; too much effort in design</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

