<h2 id="beware-the-big-button-trap">Beware the big button trap</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Where do they go?
    <ul>
      <li>Uninformative labels on buttons; lots of room for extra text!
        <ul>
          <li>Try to provide extra text to explain the purpose of each button (e.g. beside the button)</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>‚Äã	<img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/79521972/194766780-a7fb57b7-95c7-4593-8880-214d20a21785.png" alt="image" /></p>

<p><br /></p>

<h2 id="modes">Modes</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Lock to prevent accidental use ‚Ä¶
    <ul>
      <li>remove lock : ‚Äòc‚Äô + ‚Äòyes‚Äô to confirm</li>
      <li>frequent practiced action</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>If lock forgotten
    <ul>
      <li>in pocket ‚Äòyes‚Äô gets pressed</li>
      <li>goes to phone book</li>
      <li>in phone book ‚Ä¶</li>
      <li>‚Äòc‚Äô ‚Äì delete entry</li>
      <li>‚Äòyes‚Äô ‚Äì confirm</li>
      <li>‚Ä¶ oops !</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

